    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-04-07T23:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-04-07T23:00:00-05:00" n="836"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d836">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">710.J/4–748: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d836fn1">Secretary <persName corresp="#p_MGC1"
                            >Marshall</persName> was at Bogotá attending the Ninth International
                        Conference of American States, March 30–May 2, 1948.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-04-07T23:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 7, 1948—11 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Martel1">Martel</gloss> 26. Personal for <persName
                        corresp="#p_LRA1">Lovett</persName> from <persName corresp="#p_MGC1"
                        >Marshall</persName>. Reference <gloss target="#t_Telmar1">Telmar</gloss>
                        29<note n="2" xml:id="d836fn2">Not printed; it summarized paragraph 7 of
                            <gloss target="#t_Delsec1">Delsec</gloss> 1658, <hi rend="italic"
                            >supra</hi> (710.J/4–648).</note> regarding Austria: I am concerned lest
                    we be put clearly in position of thwarting conclusion of Austrian treaty. What
                    are the odds between general world effect of concluding treaty and risk of
                    Soviet subversion of government following withdrawal of troops?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_MGC1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
